sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User
participant App as Commit History Webview
participant Router as HistoryMessageRouter
participant Registry as RepositoryRegistry
participant UseCase as GetCommitHistoryUseCase
participant Repo as GitRepository implements GitHistoryOperations
participant Runtime as HybridGitRuntime
participant Cli as CliGitRuntime

User->>App: Open Commit History
App->>Router: history/dataRequest(repositoryLocator, PageRequest, filters, requestId)
Router->>Registry: resolveRepository(repositoryLocator)
Registry-->>Router: Repo
Router->>UseCase: execute(Repo, filters, PageRequest, signal)
UseCase->>Repo: getCommitGraph(filters, PageRequest, signal)
Repo->>Runtime: getCommitGraph(executionContext, filters, PageRequest, signal)
Runtime->>Cli: getCommitGraph(executionContext, filters, PageRequest, signal)
Cli-->>Runtime: Page(GitCommit)
Runtime-->>Repo: Page(GitCommit)
Repo-->>UseCase: Page(GitCommit)
UseCase-->>Router: Page(HistoryCommit)
Router-->>App: history/dataResponse(requestId, Page(HistoryCommit))
App-->>User: Render first cursor page

User->>App: Click Load More
App->>Router: history/dataRequest(repositoryLocator, NextCursorPageRequest, filters, requestId)
Router->>Registry: resolveRepository(repositoryLocator)
Registry-->>Router: Repo
Router->>UseCase: execute(Repo, filters, NextCursorPageRequest, signal)
UseCase->>Repo: getCommitGraph(filters, NextCursorPageRequest, signal)
Repo->>Runtime: getCommitGraph(executionContext, filters, NextCursorPageRequest, signal)
Runtime->>Cli: getCommitGraph(executionContext, filters, NextCursorPageRequest, signal)
Cli-->>Runtime: Page(GitCommit)
Runtime-->>Repo: Page(GitCommit)
Repo-->>UseCase: Page(GitCommit)
UseCase-->>Router: Page(HistoryCommit)
Router-->>App: history/dataResponse(requestId, Page(HistoryCommit))
App-->>User: Append cursor page
